extras.optText:
##### Calculator How-To 

This template uses *Excel* and *Windows* nodes to read operations from an excel file, 
makes calculations using calculator and writes the results to the same file.

Follow these steps to test this template;

**1.** Edit the Config Node

**2.** Set the msg.calc_path field to the relative path of calculator process according to
your PATH envrionment variable.

**3.** Set the msg.excel_path field to the full filepath of the excel file including
calculation operations.
